snippet.title: Papa's Quiz - Full Gameplay
snippet.description:
Full gameplay of the streaming friendly party game Papa's Quiz.
Available now on Apple TV: https://apps.apple.com/tt/app/papas-quiz/id1535587287
On Steam the 28th of December: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1484730/Papas_Quiz/

Soon on the Mac App Store, Playstation, and Xbox.
